  - 4 crystal forms, 16 independent molecules, 1.8 Å (Form I, P4₁2₁2), BESSY/SLS synchrotrons
  - Proposed pentameric (C₅) α-helical channel model with polar interior, nonpolar exterior
  - Intersubunit Ca²⁺/Zn²⁺ cross-links; citrate blocks by chelating these ions
  - Crystallization: Hampton/Jena/Emerald screens, MPD cryoprotection
- **checklist.csv**: Updated

