## [2026-04-28] create | imac.md — Immobilized Metal Affinity Chromatography

- **New page created**: [[imac]] — IMAC (Immobilized Metal Affinity Chromatography) for His-tag purification
  - Ni-NTA, TALON (Co2+), IDA variants
  - Typical protocol: equilibration, binding, wash (10-40 mM imidazole), elution (150-500 mM imidazole)
  - Applications in membrane protein work: E. coli, Sf9, HEK293, Pichia expression systems
  - Detergent compatibility with most non-ionic detergents (DDM, LMNG, OG, etc.)
